How to get started with AgentPhone 🤖📱

Open the app → go to Settings → tap your Profile Picture 3 times.
This will open the Redeem Code field.

Redeem whichever codes you want to use:

• MAKESOMETHINGAGENTSWANT — $15 in credits to explore the platform
• SENDAMESSAGE — a dedicated SMS + voice number with $5 in credits
• AP2IMSG — access to a shared iMessage line so your agent can send + receive iMessages

(If the shared iMessage line is full, ping me and I’ll send the next code.)

For the shared iMessage line:

• Go to Shared Lines in the menu
• Add a whitelisted contact
• That contact must send the first message to the iMessage number to initiate the thread

After that, two-way messaging works normally.

There’s also inbound calling available in testing for hackers today (from the whitelisted contact only).

If you run into any issues, ping me anytime. One note: I probably wouldn’t base your entire project around the inbound calling feature on iMessage lines yet since it’s still experimental. 

